research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:21:    "summary": "已落盘修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 override 接线，使这条新异构 MoE family 可以继续做合法的单变量 param-only 探针。建议本轮以 r129 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，用一次 matched-cost 低开销实验直接检验“shared low-rank basis + 单 routed expert local top-k”是否能把该 family 推进到新的 <0.3x Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:24:    "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:25:    "family_stage": "stabilize",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:26:    "self_review": "这轮先消除真实 blocker：r129 之后该新 family 虽已可训练，但 AutoResearch 没把它接到 expert/factorized override allowlist，导致后续单变量结构 probe 无法合法发起。真实落盘改动只在 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`，不改 trainer/eval 语义；计划运行时相对 r129 仍只改 1 个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`。风险是单 expert 路由可能让 FVU 回退到被现有 0.30x-0.34x anchor 支配；但这正是当前低开销阶段最需要回答的结构问题。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:38:      "已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 AutoResearch override allowlist；此前该 family 对 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` / `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` / `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的 param-only probe 会在训练前被判为 disallowed。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:39:      "本地校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides(..., fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk')` 现在接受 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，同时仍拒绝不属于该 family 的 `TRUNK_RANK`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:43:      "如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 在约 0.29x 下仍接近 r129 的 FVU，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 或 `128`，继续压 shared scorer 成本。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:44:      "如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显掉点，则说明该 family 的瓶颈更像 routed capacity 而非 active path 过长；下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 做 matched-cost 对照，而不是回到旧 family。",
