research/history/round_summaries/round_0192.json:39:      "如果这轮在约 0.20x 下显著优于 r190，下一轮优先继续留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO` 来校准 shared coarse 与 residual cleanup 的预算分配。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0192.json:40:      "如果这轮仍明显弱于 `<0.25x` anchors，则可基本结束这条 trunk-free shared-coarse+expert-cleanup 低成本槽位，把预算转回别的 architecture-level probe。"
