research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。最终重构公式可写为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `{u_i}` 是由共享低秩 basis 导出的静态 shared 向量库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert 的静态子库原子；在线侧先通过轻量 shared bottleneck / router 得到 shared 分支系数与少量激活 expert，再在对应静态库上做有限加权和。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 查表/加权和 + routed expert 子库查表 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前 round 172 的主问题不是继续在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上补 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 插值，而是寻找一个新的 `<0.25x` 结构槽位来挑战现有 low-cost anchor。相对 r171 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=96`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，直接回答“在相同轻 trunk + 轻 routed recipe 下，加回一个更便宜的 shared bottleneck 分支，是否比纯 `lowrank_expert_topk` 更值得”。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:20:    "summary": "以 r171 为 reference，仅切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，在保持 `K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 不变的前提下，执行一个新的 matched-cost low-cost architecture probe，测试 `shared bottleneck + expert-specific head` 是否能在约 `0.22x` 成本下优于当前同带 anchors。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:23:    "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:30:        "value": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:36:      "`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的导出形式仍是静态 shared 低秩库加静态 routed expert 子库上的有限加权和，应按 LUTurbo `扩展兼容` 处理。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:38:      "相较于 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 已经出现的更强低成本负信号，`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 仍保留更高的信息价值，因为它只对 shared 分支做 low-rank 化，而没有继续 factorize routed experts。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:53:    "architecture": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
