research/history/round_summaries/round_0203.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_shared(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(x)} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}\u3002\u5176\u4e2d B^sh \u4e0e {B_e} \u90fd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u5c11\u91cf routed expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u5fc5\u8981\u65f6\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\u7684 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1bbatch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u4e3b\u7ebf\u3002\u5f53\u524d incumbent r199 \u7684 objective=0.386114 \u5904\u4e8e cost=0.19x\u3001exceed=0.196114 \u7684\u5e73\u8861\u5e26\uff0c\u800c recent \u4e24\u4e2a\u7ed3\u6784 probe\uff08r200 lowrank_expert_topk\u3001r202 shared_two_stage_residual_expert\uff09\u90fd\u6ca1\u628a objective \u62c9\u4e0b\u53bb\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u8fd9\u4e9b\u7ed3\u6784\u4e0a\u52a0\u4e00\u70b9 shared/coarse \u8fd8\u4e0d\u591f\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r159 \u4ec5\u628a ACTIVE_EXPERTS \u4ece 2 \u964d\u5230 1\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5 shared+routed \u5bb6\u65cf\u6700\u5173\u952e\u3001\u4e14\u5f53\u524d target \u8fd8\u6ca1\u5728\u8fd9\u6761 low-cost lane \u4e0a\u56de\u7b54\u7684\u95ee\u9898: \u5982\u679c shared \u5206\u652f\u771f\u7684\u80fd\u5403\u6389\u5e73\u6ed1\u4e3b\u5e72\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 routed path \u538b\u6210\u5355 expert \u540e\uff0ctotal_cost_ratio \u53ef\u4ece\u7ea6 0.21x \u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u964d\u5230\u7ea6 0.17x\uff0c\u540c\u65f6 exceed \u4e0d\u5e94\u50cf\u65e7\u7684\u9ad8\u5bbd\u5ea6\u5355\u8def probe \u90a3\u6837\u660e\u663e\u5931\u63a7\u3002\u82e5\u8be5\u5047\u8bbe\u6210\u7acb\uff0c\u8fd9\u4f1a\u5f62\u6210\u4e00\u4e2a\u65b0\u7684\u66f4\u9760\u5de6 objective \u6bb5\uff1b\u82e5\u4e0d\u6210\u7acb\uff0c\u5219\u53ef\u66f4\u5e72\u51c0\u5730\u5224\u5b9a\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a shared+routed \u7684\u6536\u76ca\u4ecd\u4f9d\u8d56\u53cc expert active path\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:35:      "r218 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5f97\u5230 objective=0.437249\u3001cost=0.214844\u3001exceed=0.222406\uff1br219 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` \u5f97\u5230 objective=0.435236\u3001cost=0.214844\u3001exceed=0.220392\u3002shared-lowrank \u7ebf\u5728\u5f53\u524d matched recipe \u4e0b\u5df2\u7ecf\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u6e05\u6670\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0076.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。相对 r65 仅把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 32 提到 64，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`TRUNK_RANK=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，直接回答当前低成本三段式结构的核心未决问题：如果 r65 在约 0.49x 带的瓶颈仍有一部分来自 routed expert 子库总容量不足，而不只是 trunk 宽度或 residual cleanup 配比，那么扩大总静态 expert 容量、同时保持 active path 不变，应能在近同一 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并把 `lowrank + expert + residual` 这条兼容结构前沿进一步向下推进。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0141.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0141.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r123 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变，直接做一次 matched-cost hetero-MoE 结构对照，回答“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local head”这条线在约 0.30x total_cost 下是否能形成比当前 low-cost anchor 更有价值的新结构段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0141.json:20:    "summary": "建议以 r123 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。这是一轮面向低成本前沿的 matched-cost 结构对照，用当前最相关的 low-cost anchor 直接回答“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local top-k”是否值得继续，而不是继续在最近连续失利的 residual 变体上做局部压缩。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0141.json:23:    "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0141.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 已连续两轮未形成新非支配点后，继续沿同一 family 做 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `K` 的局部扫参信息增量偏低；切回 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 做 matched-cost architecture swap，更符合当前“结构扩展优先”和对 hetero MoE 的明确优先级。主要风险是该 family 先前在更高容量配方下已有负信号；但当前这次是更低成本、与 low-cost anchor 严格对照的重验，结论会更清晰。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0141.json:30:        "value": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"
