research/history/round_summaries/round_0232.json:36:      "Round 230 `two_stage_residual_expert@K32` \u7ed9\u51fa `objective=0.586051 / cost=0.414062x / exceed=0.171988 / fvu=0.146965`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u53bb\u6389 trunk \u540e cleanup \u6536\u76ca\u4ecd\u5728\uff0c\u4f46\u4e0d\u5982 `lowrank_expert_residual`\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0184.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `factorized_expert_topk`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}`，其中 `h(x)=ReLU(Bx)` 是共享低维投影，`E(h(x))` 是轻量 router 选出的少量 active experts，`{b_{e,i}}` 是各 expert 的静态子库原子；在线侧可直接导出为“shared low-rank projection + 轻量 expert 路由 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权求和”的 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能作历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。r183 的新 family `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 在约 `0.24x` 下仅做到 `FVU=0.1411`，说明“shared coarse trunk + routed residual cleanup”这条 two-stage 变体没有打败现有 low-cost anchor；因此下一步更高信息量的问题不是继续在 shared/coarse 线上补参数，而是转向当前高优先级但尚未在这条 exact low-cost recipe 上 fresh 验证的“expert 内部 low-rank / small head”槽位。相对 r176 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“把 routed-only expert 的 full-dim 局部 scorer 换成 shared bottleneck + expert-specific small head，能否在更低总成本下修复 r176 的质量缺口”。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0184.json:38:      "r183 的 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 已在约 `0.24x` 失败并归档，当前不应继续沿 shared-coarse two-stage 线做局部参数补点。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0132.json:7:  "family_name": "two_stage_residual_expert",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0132.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(r_1)}(r_1)} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 r_1 = x - Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i；B={b_i} 是静态 coarse library，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库，e(r_1) 是轻量 router 选择的单个 expert。在线侧可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“coarse 查表 + expert residual 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `two_stage_residual_expert` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r131 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到 `two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答在当前 <0.5x 带里，去掉 low-rank trunk、改用“coarse global library + local expert residual”是否比单 expert `lowrank + expert` 更值得继续；如果该 trunk-free staged 结构在约 0.47x total_cost 下显著优于 r131 的 FVU=0.1640，则说明当前低到中成本带更缺的是 staged residual 修正，而不是进一步压 trunk/router。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0132.json:20:    "summary": "Round 132 建议做一次高信息量的 matched-architecture probe，而不是继续沿 `lowrank_expert_*` 微调。以 r131 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=two_stage_residual_expert`，用同一训练配方直接测试 trunk-free staged residual 结构能否在当前低到中成本带形成新的 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0132.json:23:    "family_name": "two_stage_residual_expert",
